> How much time I am allowed to spend in the soudnfunc hook ?
> I do mixing some audiostreams to fill the next (short) buffer.

You should only change the playbuffer to your last calculate one and do a
software interrupt and calc your new data to the last free buffer.Tasks are
not dropout stable but for debugging you can also signal a task and
calculate data from here.



